    <string name="about_howtoplay"><b>How to play:</b>\nThe goal of the game is to correctly mark all fields where the bombs are and uncover all number fields. Each field on the board is either a bomb or number field, which displays amount of bombs in 8 nearby fields.\n\n<b>Controls:</b>\nTap on empty field to uncover it. Be careful, if you click on the bomb, it will explode.\nTap and hold on empty field to mark it as a bomb. Holding on number field will uncover nearby fields if the bombs around it are correctly marked. However if they are not - unmarked bomb will explode. </string>
